title: Best Of (Seahawks stun Russ and Broncos, Dak may be back soon, Steph would have welcomed KD back to Warriors)
description:
00:00 Seahawks stun Broncos after Denver loses on a controversial field goal. Is Russell Wilson worth that big contract?
11:19 Should the Cowboys try and find a replacement for Dak after the news that he won’t be out for as long as originally suggested?
30:07 Steph Curry said in a recent interview he was more than happy to re-unite with Kevin Durant. Who is the misunderstood player?
